Core features:
 - Consider hardware antialiasing options
 - Data structure and arrays description
 - Configurable per-output pipeline clear color
 - Configurable depth buffer properties
 - Viewport/scissor configuration
 - Indiced vertex mode

Build process:
 - Automatic release packaging on windows

Examples:
 - Basic text rendering
 - 3D movement with mouselook+WASD
 - Different materials on a scene
 - Shadow maps
 - Toon shader
 - Interactive 3D function plot
 - Port terrain heightmap (?)

Feature-level bugs:
 - Function naming: Polygon vs Primitive